data.description:
This charming 3 bed 2 bath home has everything to make you feel at home and cozy. 
Has a wonderful open floor plan. New floors and paint with lots of windows for great light. Backyard has endless possibilities. Great for entertaining.

Closing contingent on seller finding suitable replacement home.
